Package dalserver.tap

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdqlQueryImpl
    DALServer implementation of the OpenCADC AdqlQuery class, used to translate an ADQL query to native SQL for the back-end, and verify it in the process.
    BasicUploadManager  
    DbmsTable
    This class provides methods for writing database tables, including creating a table, saving a ResultSet to a table, and related utilities for generat a basic TAP Schema.
    InlineContentHandlerImpl
    Basic ResultStore implementation usable by the cadcTAP QueryRunner for async result storage.
    MaxRecValidatorImpl
    This class controls the maximum number of records to be returned in a single request.
    ResultStoreImpl
    Basic ResultStore implementation usable by the cadcTAP QueryRunner for async result storage.
    TapJobManager
    UWS JobManager implementation for the DALServer TAP service.
    TapParamSet
    Construct an initial default parameter set containing the parameters for Table Access Protocol (TAP) service.
    TapQueryRunner
    UWS JobRunner for the TAP query.
    TapSchema
    This class provides methods to create and populate a TAP_SCHEMA instance.
    TapSchemaDS
    Given a DataSource to a TAP_SCHEMA, returns a TapSchema object containing the TAP_SCHEMA data.
    TapTableWriter
    DALServer implementation of the OpenCADC/TAP TableWriter interface.
    TapWebService
    WebService implementation for VOSI-availability.
